ong as he could, until he finally had to admit there was no evidence of a Russian collusion with Trump. The propaganda forced down our throats for years turned out to not be true and was perpetuated by the CIA.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 529}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASFvUFPRz", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 48, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8442673, "raw_content": "Tomorrow at the very beginning of the State of the Union, a Senator needs to make a motion to Vote on the Save Act. Another Senator seconds and JD Vance as the President of the Senate calls for the vote to begin. If there are less than 35 democrats on the floor because of their boycott we can win the vote at 60%.\n\n85 x 60% = 51 50 yes votes plus JD Vance = 51\n\nThey need to do it quick in case there are Democrats nearby who could race to the floor.\n\nPrecedent has been set. I can't name any, but remember all the sneaky bills they have slipped in, in the dead of the night.", "author": "bratt", "created": 1771902858618, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DrinkTeaNotKoolaid", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Can we have the SAVE act vote during the State of the Union? A number of Democrats will be boycotting the SOTU. Chip Roy says there are 50R votes", "last_comment_created": 1771905424684, "content": "<p>Tomorrow at the very beginning of the State of the Union, a Senator needs to make a motion to Vote on the Save Act. Another Senator seconds and JD Vance as the President of the Senate calls for the vote to begin. If there are less than 35 democrats on the floor because of their boycott we can win the vote at 60%.</p>\n<p>85 x 60% = 51 50 yes votes plus JD Vance = 51</p>\n<p>They need to do it quick in case there are Democrats nearby who could race to the floor.</p>\n<p>Precedent has been set. I can't name any, but remember all the sneaky bills they have slipped in, in the dead of the night.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 49, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2025669811301470643", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASFvUEr9c", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 66, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8442448, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1771896584348, "profile_picture": "o9rQiLRpoh9n", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Ucanifuthink2", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASFvUEr9c.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/katkanada_tm/status/2025669811301470643", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "A lot of people have done the worst thing that you could do.", "last_comment_created": 1771899589905, "content": "", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 67, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 64, "created": 1771792292000, "